{
  "stem": "24111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the Germans occupied Yugoslavia in April of 1941 and I arrived in the late part of November.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know? 1940.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'40.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had four months of freedom in Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During those four months, transports were organized from the Yugoslavian Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which means they rented all the ships on the Danube.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By ships, please don't think big ships.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I meant very small paddle wheelers which went down the Danube to the Black Sea, made their way to the Bosphorus, to Turkey, and finally tried to get to Palestine, which was under the British mandate.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a terrible policy of holding up the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But a few ships made it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Jewish community, Aron Menczer-- Joschko Indig, they tried to organize transports.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they concentrated, let's say, 100 children or 20 adults, a little boat, a little ship, a willing captain with lot of money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was not cheap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They Didn't do it out of the goodness of their hearts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in matter of fact, the last transport of 94 children, I was still there when they went to Belgrade and to the boat on the Danube.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And every one of those 94 children made it to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I met them in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were very active in the creation of the state of Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Unfortunately, this open door closed on the day Germany occupied Yugoslavia, in April of '41.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "From that moment on, there was no escape going down the Danube.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because the war started with Greece, Turkey, and this opening closed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I forgot to tell you too, in the four months period of time of liberty, my mother and I were able to get in contact with my father in South America.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father died shortly thereafter, in 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
